column1: #Text=With many venues reporting sell-out shows , the 68th year of the Edinburgh Festival attracted visitors from around the globe .
#Text=Wikinews ' Brian McNeil roamed the city for the four weeks of the event , capturing the colour , spectacle , and comedy , in photos .
#Text=The image gallery below may take some time to load on slower connections .
#Text=You may click on the first image to view the images with the new Mediawiki Media Viewer ; again , full-size/full-screen images may take time to load .
